OL,3,CWarm Welcome Spaces scheme returns to
OL,4,CJersey's Town Church
OL,6,FThe church is open between 9am and
OL,7,F6pm, Monday to Friday, and during the
OL,8,Fafternoons at the weekend.
OL,10,FWhen the scheme is running, the church
OL,11,Fis split into zones depending on a
OL,12,Fvisitor's needs - there is a "work"
OL,13,Fzone with WIFI available, a "rest &
OL,14,Frecharge" zone where you can get hot
OL,15,Fdrinks, and a "play" zone for pre-
OL,16,Fschool aged children.
