OL,4,CJersey's Town Church
OL,6,FKatie adds: "We have lots of young
OL,7,Ffamilies who come down during the day,
OL,8,Fsome with additional needs who find it
OL,9,Fdifficult to be somewhere which is
OL,10,Fbusy.
OL,12,F"They've valued greatly being able to
OL,13,Fcome down during the day and enable
OL,14,Ftheir children to play."
OL,16,FAlthough the project was originally
OL,17,Fset up to help people with the cost of
OL,18,Fliving crisis, it has also acted as a
OL,19,Fway of battling loneliness.
